                            <comment id="14679850" author="dashorst" created="Mon, 10 Aug 2015 09:28:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think the ResourceUtils.getLocaleFromFilename(String path) has the order of locale and minimization wrong:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It currently parses: File.min_Lang_Coun_Var.ext while the typical convention is File_Lang_Coun_Var.min.ext&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Surely considering the ResourceUtils.getMinifiedName() method which does work according to convention.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am working on a patch that fixes this, and also makes PathLocale have more information regarding the filename.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
